{"tid":1861733,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"<突發> 義診中醫師捱唔住就嚟要執笠 2","createTime":"2020-02-04T09:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T04:38:09.000Z","uid":77001,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebfec48b71d3d51a518781972ae81a4bc3ff53c","tid":1861733,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"我上個post講完去咗位中醫度睇tg咳<br />\n睇咗2次+做針灸 已經好返曬<br />\n今日再上去睇 脊椎骨頭移位<br />\n醫師同我講已經蝕咗半年租<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為診所係鵝頸橋，次次都好大影響，d客都上唔到去<br />\n4萬蚊月租，佢就黎捱唔住要執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有做過cnn訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不斷支援受傷手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=h-D8JLV66vM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh-D8JLV66vM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=4d042a83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=h-D8JLV66vM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/04/170813_28a9218b5b5e5c9589f194ed371a4ab8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F04%2F170813_28a9218b5b5e5c9589f194ed371a4ab8.png&h=a6a330f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/04/170814_a983dbd8afc621176b89642f447b640d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F04%2F170814_a983dbd8afc621176b89642f447b640d.png&h=f3ef021e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/04/170816_08dcb9495160ec8c03550c87e18ce90e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F04%2F170816_08dcb9495160ec8c03550c87e18ce90e.png&h=207a4c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個咁好咁叻嘅中醫師都一直陪住大家<br />\n<br />\n我唔想佢成為condom呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中醫師都係醫護手足黎架<br />\n大家可唔可以介紹下俾身邊嘅人上去睇病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f5521934c8d1499a1a0582ab411366aea4f33067","tid":1861733,"uid":77001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"只要你打去預約 醫師就好夜都會等你<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腰頸脊椎$300-500 我睇左$400<br />\n藥粉$70日 淨係知道咁多<br />\n<br />\n仲開到醫生紙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kwan60905678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkwan60905678&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=3eec42b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kwan60905678</a>"},{"pid":"764a7ef2876544c0838c60db60c6748e3b41413d","tid":1861733,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4255fd7db3fcef3d5c248f9f9337113b0a4c7b4b","tid":1861733,"uid":236017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9f36b55aef60f6864f82fbae1fe4383b07d7f19","tid":1861733,"uid":6370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"脊椎移位都可以睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7b76be58d7eb97a2ed332f967cb4612275f82a","tid":1861733,"uid":77001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggDzJ4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggDzJ4k.png&h=ea9f798b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFtv1Q8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFtv1Q8.png&h=ee4a71c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b55a7f202c081449503c0a61768ec654d6e21205","t